OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FSome patchy cloud to the east
OL,6,Ffirst thig in the morning. This will
OL,7,Fclear quickly, leaving another bright
OL,8,Fand sunny day. Winds lighter than
OL,9,FWednesday allowing temperatures to
OL,10,Fclimb further. UV levels will also be
OL,11,Fhigh.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FA clear night to come with
OL,14,Flight winds, allowing some mist and
OL,15,Ffog patches to develop in prone spots.
OL,16,FCloud returning in the east, with a
OL,17,Fgrass frost in places.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
