OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FAny mist and fog will clear
OL,6,Fquickly as low cloud in the east
OL,7,Ffades. Another bright and sunny day
OL,8,Fexpected with temperatures slightly
OL,9,Fhigher than Thursday.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FStaying
OL,12,Fwarm and sunny into the weekend with
OL,13,Flight winds. Likely to be more cloud
OL,14,Fon Sunday which will allow
OL,15,Ftemperatures to dip slightly.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
